title: Art Blakey-Hold On I'm Coming (LP Rip)
description:
320 Kbit/s mp3, Original 1966 Limelight Label US Edition LP Rip,

another great classic from my mothers LP collection. Fabulous Art Blakey with a lot of friends at their best. Especially their version of Loving Spoonful's "Daydream". Once you hear it, it doesn't get out of your head. So biggie up and respect to my mother and the allmighty Jah for creating her and that Art Blakey guy and his friends.Enjoy!
